snippet.title: Disney Apologizes to Johnny Depp (Shocking Settlement)
snippet.description:
Disney Apologizes to Johnny Depp (Shocking Settlement)

So, I'm sure we all know about the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard drama by now.

Amber and Johnny have been going back and forth about lies Amber told the media.

Now come on, we all knew Johnny was innocent!

Even Disney is now apologizing to him!

What exactly happened and what are they offering Johnny?

Watch the whole video to find out! And don't forget to subscribe and like :)

#johnnydepp #disney #amberheard
